Description: An R Database Interface (DBI) compatible interface to several database platforms 
    using Java Database Connectivity (JDBC). Supported platforms are
    PostgreSQL, Oracle, Microsoft SQL Server, Amazon Redshift, Google BigQuery, Snowflake, Spark.
SystemRequirements: Java (>= 8)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
